{"id": "1450706727715475539", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "905807477520609321", "author_name": "shangxianyue_sp", "author_bot": false, "content": "我有一个想法\n如何优雅地把凯刻斯骗到床上并榨干\n就说守密人的精华可以觉醒血脉\n但是单纯的精华效果有限\n需要进行源于磐龙古国高原地区的双修密法\n直接口教刚教变成守密人的X奴隶", "timestamp": "2025-12-17T04:30:36.715000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
