{"id": "1450803011889922048", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "905807477520609321", "author_name": "shangxianyue_sp", "author_bot": false, "content": "我觉得守密人的精华相较于咖啡还是有优点的\n咖啡苦，需要加糖；守密人的精华成分里就含糖\n金木研想喝咖啡还得去安定区，或者自己手磨；守密人可以直接把巨龙怼进杜勒赛因的嘴里\n伙计们，你们觉得我说的对吗？", "timestamp": "2025-12-17T10:53:12.651000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1450814460699611300", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "905807477520609321", "author_name": "shangxianyue_sp", "author_bot": false, "content": "不过我后来发现最不可思议的是\n1.ccg竟然也搞人体试验搞混种食尸鬼\n2.变成食尸鬼后似乎还有生育能力\n3.利世的遗产竟然还有治愈效果", "timestamp": "2025-12-17T11:38:42.260000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
