{"id": "1450823098868957280", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "905807477520609321", "author_name": "shangxianyue_sp", "author_bot": false, "content": "我有一个想法\n前几天我提到了隔壁的同类的新月同行倒闭的事情\n认真的讲\n很少有游戏能做到有始有终\n新月同行也不例外\n忘却能比新月同行强的一点是\n开头和结尾\n新月同行开头也要求调查员写遗书的\n但只有两句话\n忘却是两章\n除开校猫这个因素外\n忘却能活到现在也是能认真一点点的\n校猫最拟人的一次", "timestamp": "2025-12-17T12:13:01.760000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-12-17T12:16:47.731000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1450833397541769216", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "944524613168279553", "author_name": "ena04564", "author_bot": false, "content": "新月是因為母公司出問題吧\n忘卻原本就做好可能收掉的打算", "timestamp": "2025-12-17T12:53:57.155000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1450833914540326953", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "905807477520609321", "author_name": "shangxianyue_sp", "author_bot": false, "content": "我有一个想法\n目前来看\n星辰正位时刻到像是压缩版的忘却前夜\n明年的主线大概会是勒姆瓦希沙漠地区\n在忘却篇里\n威廉就是在勒姆瓦希跨越维度的\n根据编年史\n弥萨格三位创始人之一的\n刻拉尔克什也在勒姆瓦希地区失踪\n华徳去世，塔薇在忘却维度\n那么在星辰篇里\n有可能会遇到这位刻拉尔克什\n另有\n还有一个问题待解答\n威廉的好友芬格尔的死亡是不是也与维度穿越和提灯教会有关系？", "timestamp": "2025-12-17T12:56:00.417000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1450842414968209501", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "259018461458595850", "author_name": "amstelredam", "author_bot": false, "content": "聯動新月同行可以拓展一下4v4相位玩法嗎\n我討厭競爭  但我好喜歡相位的卡 我想玩PVE⋯⋯", "timestamp": "2025-12-17T13:29:47.077000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1450842541304971355", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "259018461458595850", "author_name": "amstelredam", "author_bot": false, "content": "但不要學新月站位綁承傷⋯", "timestamp": "2025-12-17T13:30:17.198000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
